== Sightseeing ==

* Hiroshima Prefecture: Hiroshima, Miyajima, Fukuyama, Onomichi
* Okayama Prefecture: Okayama, Kurashiki, Takahashi, Tsuyama, Niimi, Bizen, Tamano
